{"word":"ἀποδιδράσκω","slug":"ἀποδιδράσκω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀποδιδράσκω</b></el> <p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to run away</i> or <i>off, escape</i>, or <i>flee from</i>, <a href='S:especially'>esp.</a> <i>by stealth</i>, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, attic; of runaway slaves, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>; of soldiers, <i>to desert</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a> <i>to flee, shun</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}